41:["$","p","83",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Best for:"}]," Visual collaboration, brainstorming, and workshops."]}]
42:["$","p","85",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Miro's infinite canvas enables remote teams to brainstorm, diagram, and plan visually. Templates for retrospectives, user story mapping, and design sprints accelerate collaboration."]}]
43:["$","p","87",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I like:"}]," Miro replaces the physical whiteboard in a way that actually works remotely. G2 users rate Miro 91% for visual collaboration. One remote facilitator noted: \"Miro makes our remote retrospectives and design sprints as engaging as in-person sessions.\" The template library is extensive."]}]
44:["$","p","89",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I don't like:"}]," Large boards can become visually cluttered. The free plan limits boards to three, which is restrictive for active teams."]}]
45:["$","p","91",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Pricing:"}]," Free (3 boards); Team $16/user/month; Business $30/user/month."]}]
