47:["$","p","95",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Best for:"}]," Measuring and improving employee engagement in distributed teams."]}]
48:["$","p","97",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Culture Amp is the leading employee experience platform, helping remote teams measure engagement, identify issues, and take action before attrition."]}]
49:["$","p","99",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I like:"}]," Culture Amp's surveys are research-backed and benchmarked against industry standards. The \"eNPS\" (employee Net Promoter Score) is a single number that gives leadership a pulse on team sentiment. G2 users rate Culture Amp 88% for survey analytics."]}]
4a:["$","p","101",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I don't like:"}]," Culture Amp is a measurement tool — it tells you what's wrong but doesn't fix it. You need to take action based on the data."]}]
