4e:["$","p","109",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["Every Time Zone is a simple, free tool that shows team members' working hours across time zones in a single visual interface."]}]
4f:["$","p","111",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I like:"}]," It's free and instantly useful. The visual slider shows overlapping working hours at a glance. G2 users rate it 4.5/5, with one remote manager saying: \"Every Time Zone saved me from scheduling meetings at midnight for my APAC team.\""]}]
