52:["$","p","117",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"Best for:"}]," Secure password and credential management distributed teams."]}]
53:["$","p","119",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["1Password helps distributed teams share credentials securely, manage MFA tokens, and enforce password policies across the organization."]}]
54:["$","p","121",{"className":"text-[#8BA3BE] leading-relaxed mb-4 text-base","children":["",["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-bold text-[#F0F4F8]","children":"What I like:"}]," 1Password's shared vaults make it easy to give team members access to the tools they need without sharing passwords via Slack or email. G2 users rate 1Password 4.7/5, and one security-conscious CTO noted: \"1Password is our most-used tool after Slack. Every credential, every API key, every admin login lives there.\""]}]
